e reinsurance contract held                     by the whole amount of the change in the fulfilment cash flows of this                     reinsurance contract held of CU15 from CU(25) to CU(10). This is because the                     whole change in the fulfilment cash flows allocated to the group of underlying                     insurance contracts adjusts the contractual service margin of those underlying                     insurance contracts.</p></li></ol>             </entry></row></tbody></tgroup></table></body></paragraph>